, thanks.<br><br> <p>Valas Defai</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F5F5DC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uniyaranyteshade.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Niyara Nyteshade</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 58<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/26/01 4:57:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335dragonsandtheplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=568.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.nemesys-guild.com/board/niya_side.jpg width=125 height=218 ></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: My solution to solving the open raid problem</span><hr size=1> >>Basically, there are too many "Open" raids booked on the calandar<<<br><br>Basically, you're the only person I've seen complaining about the number of open raids on the calendar.  So there aren't too many, <b>you</b> just think there are.<br><br>I'm truly not trying to be a bitch here, but why don't you stop wasting time and energy on this battle that you cannot win, and start making arrangements to attend some of the Open Raids in question?<br><br><br> <p><img src="http://www.nemesys-guild.com/board/niya_sig.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ucyriccs.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cyricc S</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 26<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/26/01 8:10:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335dragonsandtheplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=568.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Open raid problem?</span><hr size=1> hehe...Open raid problem?<br><br>16 is too much?<br><br>God is wasted?<br><br>I've really only seen you having a problem with it, and I don't think 16 is too much, and if the god is